         <div class="bordered-sidebar-content without-sidebar">
          <h3 class="title">
           PhD Graduate Study
          </h3>
          <div class="main">
           <img alt="./tab-header" class="flush-top pull-none pull-md-left" src="images/homepage/programs/phd-program.jpg"/>
           <div class="flush-top-recursive">
            <p>
             PhD students at Segal work in the Design Cluster, an interdisciplinary doctoral cluster program jointly sponsored by Segal, the
             <a href="http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="Visit the McCormick School of Engineering website">
              McCormick School of Engineering
             </a>
             , and
