            </li>
           </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="main">
           <img alt="./tab-header" class="flush-top pull-none pull-md-left" src="images/homepage/programs/exec-ed.jpg"/>
           <div class="flush-top-recursive">
            <p>
             The Segal Design Institute has partnered with the
             <a href="http://www.kellogg.northwestern.edu/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="Kellogg School of Management">
              <span>
               Kellogg School of Management
              </span>
             </a>
             to offer two dynamic programs for mid- to senior-level executives created to catalyze innovation through design thinking.
            </p>
            <p>
             <a class="button" href="programs/executive-education.html">
              Learn more
